Sanitize version 0.01
=====================

This module offers simple ways to sanitize or validate string inputs against a number of possible criteria.

Example usage:

use Sanitize;
print sanitize("This is my ip: 10.0.0.1:80", ip => 1);
print validate("invalid@email!something", email => 1);

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  none

